{"tha-ap146:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap146:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap146:0.3":"Saparivariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap146:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap146:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap146:1.3":"Jalitva aggikkhandhova, ","tha-ap146:1.4":"sambuddho parinibbuto. ","tha-ap146:2.1":"Nibbute ca mahavire, ","tha-ap146:2.2":"thupo vitthariko ahu; ","tha-ap146:2.3":"Duratova upatthenti, ","tha-ap146:2.4":"dhatugehavaruttame. ","tha-ap146:3.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap146:3.2":"akam candanavedikam; ","tha-ap146:3.3":"Dissati thupakhandho ca, ","tha-ap146:3.4":"thupanucchaviko tada. ","tha-ap146:4.1":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap146:4.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap146:4.3":"Omattam me na passami, ","tha-ap146:4.4":"pubbakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap146:5.1":"Pancadasakappasate, ","tha-ap146:5.2":"ito attha jana ahum; ","tha-ap146:5.3":"Sabbe samattanama te, ","tha-ap146:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap146:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap146:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap146:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap146:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saparivariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap146:8.1":"Saparivariyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}